<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ن ف ي:</span> نَفَاهُ طَرَدَهُ وَبَابُهُ رَمَى،<span class="c5"> يُقَالُ:</span> نَفَاهُ <span class="c2">(فَانْتَفَى)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(نَفَى)</span> أَيْضًا يَتَعَدَّى وَيَلْزَمُ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ الْقُطَامِيُّ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>فَأَصْبَحَ جَارَاكُمْ قَتِيلًا<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَ <span class="c2">(نَافِيَا)</span> أَيْ مُنْتَفِيًا.<span class="c5"> وَتَقُولُ:</span> هَذَا يُنَافِي ذَلِكَ وَهُمَا <span class="c2">(يَتَنَافَيَانِ)</span> . وَ <span class="c2">(النُّفَايَةُ)</span> بِالضَّمِّ مَا نُفِيَ مِنَ الشَّيْءِ لِرَدَاءَتِهِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>